Name: Seek Girl Ⅵ
About the game: This is a casual Sokoban game. Players need to use the keyboard to control the male character to move to the female character to complete the task and move to the next level. However, there are many pitfalls in this process. At this point, the boy needs to push the box on the map to fill the trap and continue passing. Each map may have a variety of clearance strategies. Use your wits to find the girl. The game is similar to the previous one, add more interesting levels and characters, if you like this series don't miss!
